<D>__{we're doin' okay.}
<A>__{as jules and brett talk, vincent moves behind the young guys.}
<C>__{jules}
<D>__{do you know who we are?}
<A>__{brett shakes his head: "no."}
<C>__{jules}
<D>__{we're associates of your business partner marsellus wallace, you remember your business partner dont'ya?}
<A>__{no answer.}
<C>__{jules}
