<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{jules}
<D>__{then you understand what i'm sayin'?}
<C>__{brett}
<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{jules}
<D>__{now describe what marsellus wallace looks like!}
<C>__{brett}
<P>__{(out of fear)}
<D>__{what?}
<A>__{jules takes his .45 and presses the barrel hard in brett's cheek.}
